data.name: Label10.Text
data.value: The program will sort all the files which will contain the entered keyword in the name. The files will be moved to a folder which is created by the program,the name of the folder is selected by the program.

data.name: Label15.Text
data.value: The program will automatically reorder all the files from the chosen start date on the final date. The extension of the file can also be specified, as well as the date range. The folder will be created by the program.
